Saharae 21 warrior</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uthevultgoesmoo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TheVultGoesMOO</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(5/7/01 11:07:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Favorite Weapons </span><hr size=1> I'm not uber or anything so I use some No-Drop stuff I got along the way.  1h slash is my main but I can't stress the importance of keeping up all yer skills or you'll be lvl 40 trying to work piercing, 1h blunt and 2h blunt kinda like this dorf i knew... Anyhoo I use a Chaleki tail (9/19 procs strong disease, comes outta dragon necro) and that 10/25 off hand the SF rogue epic mob drops <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  dunno the name of mob or the weapon, said aint it?  I used my good ol' yaks from 35-40ish but they get resisted to much.  Good 1h blunt to work w/ is a smoldering brand.  And beetle stinger / scorpiki claw impaler is a nice piercer since they're both range usable and free a bag slot.  Fellhammer if my fav 2h so far... and my 2h blunt sucks so I can't help you there.<br>
<br>
stay away from Wurmslayers they ARE EVIL!!!! *never owned one, never will <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
p.s. if yer a small race and yak's don't proc.  just get an ebon razor you'll never know the difference.  and slime coated harpoons/ kylong dagger are nice piercers<br>
<br>
Vultron Toegrind 51 Dwarf Warrior<br>
Ratba Stard 30 Cleric<br>
Defunct 13 Iksar Necro (will be lookiing for research soon) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/udiminiousmaximus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DiminiousMaximus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(5/14/01 3:39:37 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Favorite Weapons </span><hr size=1> As a warrior don't neglect any wpn skills at all.<br>
